### Install and Start Ionic Project with CLI

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/examples/ionic2/README.md

Installs the Ionic CLI globally and starts a new blank Ionic project. This is the first step to using the starter template.

```bash
sudo npm install -g ionic cordova
ionic start myBlank blank
```

