### Start MongoDB Replica Set Server

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/replication-mongodb.html

Starts a local MongoDB server configured as a replica set named 'rs0'. This is necessary for enabling MongoDB's changestream functionality, which RxDB uses for replication.

```bash
mongod --replSet rs0 --bind_ip_all
```

