### Start/Stop Appwrite Docker Instance

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/replication-appwrite.md

Commands to manage a running Appwrite instance installed via Docker Compose. 'docker-compose down' stops the instance, and 'docker-compose up' starts it. Ensure you are in the directory containing the 'docker-compose.yml' file.

```bash
# stop
docker-compose down

# start
docker-compose up
```

